description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Welcome to Rio Row' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline..
The technique difficulty is Advanced and Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Join Aisyah in Hydrow's newest Destination, Rio de Janeiro, by crushing 60-second intervals. 

Max rhythm: 34, Format: HIIT...
